          Digilent's Arty SoC based on LiteX

[> Getting started
1. Install Python3 and your vendor's software

2. Obtain LiteX and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litex --recursive
  cd litex
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

3. Obtain LiteDRAM and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litedram
  cd litedarm
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

4. Obtain LiteEth and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/liteeth
  cd liteeth
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

5. Obtain LiteScope and install it:
  git clone https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litescope
  cd litescope
  python3 setup.py develop
  cd ..

6. Build the gateware and software:
  make base (or minisoc, ddr3, etherbone)
  make load

[> Status:
BaseSoC / MiniSoC validated with 16 bits DDR3 @ 800Mbps/pin.
EtherboneSoC validated.

